.TH ILIB-WEBREPRT 1 "June 2026" "ilib @ILIB_VERSION@" "Ilib Manual"
.SH NAME
ilib-webreprt \- graph web server access-log usage
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ilib-webreprt
.RI [ options ]
.RB [ \-tod | \-dom | \-dow | \-moy ]
.I accesslog
.RI [ accesslog ...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B ilib-webreprt
parses one or more Common Log Format web server access logs and writes an
image graph of request volume to standard output. By default it produces a
time-of-day report as a line graph using all available data.
.SH OPTIONS
.SS Report type
.TP
.B \-tod
Requests by hour of the day (default).
.TP
.B \-dom
Requests by day of the month.
.TP
.B \-dow
Requests by day of the week.
.TP
.B \-moy
Requests by month of the year.
.SS Date range
.TP
.B \-all
Use all data (default).
.TP
.B \-today
.TQ
.B \-yesterday
Restrict to today / yesterday.
.TP
.B \-thisweek
.TQ
.B \-lastweek
Restrict to this / the previous Monday\(enSunday week.
.TP
.B \-thismonth
.TQ
.B \-lastmonth
Restrict to this / the previous calendar month.
.SS Presentation
.TP
.B \-line
Draw a line graph (default).
.TP
.B \-bar
Draw a bar graph instead.
.TP
.B \-nohdr
Omit the title and summary footer.
.TP
.BI \-rstring " text"
Set the label used for the retrievals being counted.
.SH EXAMPLES
.RS
.nf
ilib-webreprt -dom -bar -thismonth /var/log/apache2/access.log > usage.gif
.fi
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR ilib-index (1)
.PP
Full API documentation: https://craigk5n.github.io/ilib/
